metadata.name: Meme Gene
metadata.description:
Meme Gene's Royale Rumble!  A Burn-to-Earn collection for degens that know--> WHO will be next to enter the ring?  Who will be eliminated?  Who will survive?!   Last one left in the ring wins!  Let's Get ready to RUUUUUMBLE!!!  

Follow [https://twitter.com/SenoraBurro](url) to find out! 

Holders will participate in experiences both on and off platform and there will be plenty of chances to engage.  This is an experiment in new & emerging mint/burn/combine mechanics + human behavior + collecting... no guarantees other than fun! 

New redeem mechanisms will be added a few days after the claim period ends.

**About the artist: ** You know me. I know you. All will be revealed.  Let's have some fun.
